Description_lang: Archimonde summons a Source of Chaos at his current target that persists until it is killed.The source channels a beam at its target, pushing them away and inflicting $190706s1 Fire damage every $190703t1 sec in a straight line towards the target. This effect increases damage taken from Source of Chaos by $190706s2% for $190706d each time it inflicts damage.The amount of force pushing targets away is reduced by $s1% for each player between the source and its target.
